table of contents
for pension plans with projected benefit obligations in excess of plan assets, the projected benefit
obligation and aggregate fair value of plan assets were $3.9 billion and $3.4 billion, respectively, as of september27, 2008 and $323 million and $2 million as of september29, 2007, respectively.  the companys total accumulated pension benefit obligations at both september27, 2008 and september29, 2007 was $4.8 billion, of which
97.0% and 96.2%, respectively, were vested.  the accumulated postretirement medical benefit obligations and fair value of plan assets for
