related to sports programming rights, primarily nfl, nba, nascar, mlb and college sports.  the company has entered into operating leases
for various real estate and equipment needs, including retail outlets and distribution centers for consumer products, broadcast equipment, and office space for general and administrative purposes. rental expense for the operating leases during 2008,
2007, and 2006, including common-area maintenance and contingent rentals, was $550 million, $482 million, and $455 million, respectively.
